{"tid":1102031,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！巫師3爆出音樂涉及侵權事件！","createTime":"2019-04-11T12:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T07:22:58.000Z","uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c35012d83278cb4da5377e2a4ef8b822597c03ae","tid":1102031,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"波蘭原文:<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KrMvd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KrMvd0&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=07e6e7f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KrMvd0</a><br />\n<br />\n幾本上就是<br />\n<br />\n克羅埃西亞作曲家Elvis Stanic控告CDPR，巫師3中的一首名為Widow-Maker的音樂抄襲了<br />\n他作的Naranca這首音樂。Widow-Maker是基於Percival樂團於2012發行的Songs from the<br />\nSouthern Slavs，專輯中的Naranca這首音樂所改編的。而原作曲家已和演奏的樂團註冊了<br />\n這首音樂的版權。<br />\n<br />\nStanic表示，雖然在去年聯絡CDPR後已將單曲從各大串流媒體下架，但依然被包含在OST內<br />\n非法的銷售。他雖然很高興這首歌被用在巫師3，但對作者造成了巨大的損失。他也持續在<br />\n申請版權刪除YouTube上的音樂，但目前沒有計劃對YouTuber採取法律行動。CDPR尚未回應<br />\n此聲明，僅從OST中移除這首音樂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比較<br />\n1:01<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rMi9AiHJgaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrMi9AiHJgaU&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=594ecb29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rMi9AiHJgaU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:20<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rLNKFNRHONI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrLNKFNRHONI&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=d7ab3d2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rLNKFNRHONI</a><br />\n<br />\n醬：<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1554956113.A.41D.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FSteam%2FM.1554956113.A.41D.html&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=1afcd639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1554956113.A.41D.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3058658b771a0cf5c3f161c0466572